# NeoDMS Project Context

## What This Repo Is

**NeoDMS_v1** is a **Next.js 16 + React 19** document-management UI (**Ospyn Neo My Drive**), built on the Ospyn multi-layout template.

- **Primary product shell:** `(with-sidebar)` — dark sidebar, drive header, `#f9fafb` main surface (`.drive-shell`).
- **Default home:** `/` → `DriveDashboardPage` (greeting, Quick access, Recent Files).
- **Frontend-only:** mock data in `features/drive/` and `features/dashboard/`; no API, auth, or DB yet.
- **Template shells preserved:** `(with-header)`, `(minimal)`, `/ui-showcase` — do not remove when extending drive.

Branding & user chrome: `config/app.ts` (`productName`, `driveName`, `userDisplayName`, `workspaceName`, storage GB).

## Stack

Next.js App Router (Turbopack) · React 19 · shadcn (`radix-nova`) · Tailwind v4 · pnpm · ESLint · Prettier · strict TS · CI on `main`/PR.

