## Golden Rules

1. Thin `app/**/page.tsx` — compose `features/<feature>/components`.
2. Drive chrome in `components/layout/` (`AppSidebar`, `DocumentsAppHeader`), not in features.
3. New drive UI under `features/drive/`; do not put drive-only logic in `components/ui/`.
4. Follow `ui-component-governance.mdc` before new `components/ui/*` primitives.
5. Tables: `docs/TABLE_BEHAVIOR_GUIDE.md`. Drive visuals: `docs/DRIVE_UI_GUIDE.md`.

