## Sidebar Nav (`config/nav/sidebar-nav.ts`)

Dashboard · Owned by me · Shared with me · Shared by me · Quick access · Recent · Trash · **Settings** (footer, separate from main list).

Edit nav here only; header titles sync via `documents-app-header.tsx` `ROUTE_TITLES`.

## Layout Scoping

- `SidebarHeaderLayout` with `driveShell` in `app/(with-sidebar)/layout.tsx` applies `.drive-shell` CSS tokens (`app/globals.css`).
- Do **not** apply `.drive-shell` to `(with-header)` or `(minimal)` unless intentionally rebranding those demos.

