## Adding Drive Work

1. UI in `features/drive/components/`; mock data in `features/drive/data/`.
2. Register route under `app/(with-sidebar)/…` and `sidebar-nav.ts` + `ROUTE_TITLES`.
3. Use existing drive patterns: `QuickAccessSection`, `FileExplorerPage`, `DrivePlaceholderPage`.
4. Swap mocks for hooks/API later without changing route files.

